                </h4>
                <ul id="currentClassMembers" class="space-y-2 max-h-48 overflow-y-auto bg-white p-3 rounded-md border">
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="mt-8 flex justify-end">
            <button onclick="closeShareModal()" class="inline-block px-6 py-2.5 rounded-md font-semibold text-center uppercase tracking-wider text-sm bg-gray-600 text-white hover:bg-gray-700">Fechar</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>